1
00:01:05,079 --> 00:01:07,000
Jiang Yue, that picture...

2
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:09,280
It's okay.

3
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:11,120
Don't overthink.

4
00:01:30,879 --> 00:01:31,599
You go back first.

5
00:01:32,079 --> 00:01:32,879
I'll take care of the rest.

6
00:01:34,519 --> 00:01:35,159
Where are you going?

7
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:37,200
I'll deal with something.

8
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:38,799
I'll be back soon.

9
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,319
Take care.

10
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:16,319
This is your mom's favorite necklace.

11
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,960
Yue, keep it for me, okay?

12
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:31,400
Mom must have unspeakable pain.

13
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:33,439
But no matter what,

14
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:40,199
Black Snow will kill us sooner or later.

15
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:43,439
Just like he burned your mother to death.

16
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,000
Mom's death

17
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,319
was not caused by the arson of the Black Snow Group,

18
00:02:47,719 --> 00:02:48,240
but

19
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,439
related to that totem.

20
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:08,680
Dad,

21
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,159
I believe you,

22
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:17,319
I respect you.

23
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:20,439
I follow you.

24
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:24,639
I'm willing to let you control

25
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,159
my life.

26
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,639
But

27
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:34,400
you lied to me

28
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:36,639
about my mother's death.

29
00:03:42,080 --> 00:03:42,719
Why?

30
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:46,520
Why?

31
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:19,319
Fine.

32
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:23,560
In that case,

33
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,560
I bet you

34
00:04:36,399 --> 00:04:37,480
Lin Chuanye only has one requirement.

35
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:38,600
He likes Yunting,

36
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,639
so he wants to hold the exhibition in Yunting.

37
00:04:42,839 --> 00:04:43,759
Do as he wishes.

38
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,920
Let's get all departments to push it forward.

39
00:04:46,319 --> 00:04:46,720
Okay.

40
00:04:50,560 --> 00:04:51,519
Has Jiang Yue come yet?

41
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:54,519
No.

42
00:05:25,959 --> 00:05:27,000
Come on, baby.

43
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:29,319
Mommy will teach you how to draw a bicycle.

44
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,439
The wheels should be

45
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,160
round.

46
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,839
The wheels at the back

47
00:05:38,360 --> 00:05:39,600
are also round.

48
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,560
Look at Yue'er.

49
00:05:42,920 --> 00:05:44,000
You're doing great.

50
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,439
Yue'er.

51
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:14,399
Stop.

52
00:07:27,839 --> 00:07:30,160
Didn't you hear me go to the company?

53
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,160
I'm accompanying Qi Qi to take photos.

54
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:36,399
You know that.

55
00:07:40,040 --> 00:07:41,360
I don't need an explanation,

56
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,439
but an unconditional execution.

57
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:47,639
You'd better keep this in mind.

58
00:07:51,759 --> 00:07:52,560
Have you ever lied to me?

59
00:07:53,319 --> 00:07:54,639
What's the benefit for me to lie to you?

60
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:01,079
Send the goods safely to me in ten days,

61
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,720
and then get out of here.

62
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,199
If you ignore my words again,

63
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:09,319
I have a lot of ways to make you understand.

64
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,240
Uncle

65
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:27,319
Yes?

66
00:08:44,679 --> 00:08:45,159
Jiang Yue,

67
00:08:47,679 --> 00:08:48,480
I want to help you.

68
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,679
No matter what,

69
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,440
I can face it with you.

70
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:54,320
I want to find out the cause of my mother's death.

71
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,720
I want to know why my father lied to me.

72
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,000
But

73
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:03,759
you have your dream.

74
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:04,399
Jiang Yue,

75
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:06,120
I can't drag you into this.

76
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:09,279
This is my picture book when I was a child.

77
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:10,679
Do you want to see it?

78
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,720
Don't change the subject.

79
00:09:14,919 --> 00:09:15,840
Then I'll show you

80
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:17,080
when you want to see it.

81
00:09:20,519 --> 00:09:22,720
Don't tell anyone about the totem.

82
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,919
I'll have someone take you to school.

83
00:09:53,919 --> 00:09:55,120
Why are you looking at me like that?

84
00:09:59,279 --> 00:10:00,440
Aren't you supposed to be at school?

85
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,600
Shen Yu told me you were here, so I came.

86
00:10:03,559 --> 00:10:04,159
What are you doing here?

87
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:07,360
The results of the preliminary selection will be announced today.

88
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,440
I want to see it with you.

89
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:13,120
After all, it's the result of our joint efforts.

90
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:16,519
I just want to cheer you up.

91
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,480
Then you go there and wait for me.

92
00:10:54,279 --> 00:10:54,919
I'm not here.

93
00:10:55,519 --> 00:10:56,960
Maybe there's something wrong with the system.

94
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:58,759
I'll ask someone.

95
00:11:06,759 --> 00:11:07,240
Mr. Li

96
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:08,519
Hello.

97
00:11:09,519 --> 00:11:11,279
Pure desire

98
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:13,200
can be called the motivation to strive.

99
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,639
But Lu Qi's works

100
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,519
are dark, to put it mildly.

101
00:11:18,080 --> 00:11:19,279
They can be called evil,

102
00:11:19,639 --> 00:11:20,720
which is bad.

103
00:11:21,759 --> 00:11:22,240
I see.

104
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,519
Thank you, Mr. Li.

105
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:26,960
Evil?

106
00:11:28,159 --> 00:11:29,120
Is my work evil?

107
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:33,480
You think it's evil, too?

108
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,159
I didn't say anything.

109
00:11:38,159 --> 00:11:39,120
Then you say it.

110
00:11:39,799 --> 00:11:41,759
I think this is a true reflection of your inner self.

111
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:42,639
No.

112
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:44,919
I just want to use the most direct way

113
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:46,639
to present my inner thoughts.

114
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:49,159
Only by facing desires can one face oneself.

115
00:11:49,759 --> 00:11:50,919
It's so fitting to the theme.

116
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:52,320
How can it be evil?

117
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:55,840
Don't you even let others finish speaking?

118
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,399
You say it.

119
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,039
Whether you are evil

120
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:00,279
or dark,

121
00:12:01,039 --> 00:12:02,480
I hope your inner world

122
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,320
is full of sunshine,

123
00:12:03,320 --> 00:12:05,120
warmth, happiness and joy.

124
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:08,200
You do what you want to do.

125
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:10,200
Leave the rest to me.

126
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,759
You go home first.

127
00:12:13,879 --> 00:12:14,679
I'll go out for a while.

128
00:12:21,159 --> 00:12:22,240
Evil.

129
00:12:22,919 --> 00:12:24,360
Is it really that evil?

130
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,559
No progress in District 45 of Zone D?

131
00:12:28,799 --> 00:12:29,000
No.

132
00:12:47,759 --> 00:12:49,840
You should be preparing to deliver goods now.

133
00:12:51,240 --> 00:12:52,279
Qi Qi has a piece

134
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,159
that she wants to exhibit at the show.

135
00:12:55,039 --> 00:12:56,200
Are you negotiating with me?

136
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,159
What do you have to negotiate with me?

137
00:12:59,159 --> 00:13:00,120
If you don't agree,

138
00:13:00,879 --> 00:13:02,200
I won't deliver for you anymore.

139
00:13:02,799 --> 00:13:04,279
You want to threaten me, right?

140
00:13:06,639 --> 00:13:07,159
Jiang Yue,

141
00:13:08,879 --> 00:13:10,600
have you ever thought about

142
00:13:10,600 --> 00:13:13,120
why I've only let you deliver goods all these years?

143
00:13:13,679 --> 00:13:15,440
Because only I can make you feel at ease,

144
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:16,919
and ensure your goods

145
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,200
arrive safely.

146
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,480
If we display Qi Qi's works,

147
00:13:21,399 --> 00:13:23,440
will you still be as obedient as before?

148
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:32,000
If we display her works,

149
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,080
everything is negotiable.

150
00:13:35,039 --> 00:13:35,440
If not,

151
00:13:36,399 --> 00:13:37,039
we won't talk.

152
00:13:54,360 --> 00:13:54,720
Sir,

153
00:13:55,279 --> 00:13:56,120
it's just a photo.

154
00:13:56,799 --> 00:13:57,519
If the young master wants to display it,

155
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,440
just let him.

156
00:13:58,679 --> 00:13:59,639
I've been with you for so many years.

157
00:13:59,639 --> 00:14:00,879
Don't you understand?

158
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:04,159
Jiangyue and 3Z are my hard work

159
00:14:04,159 --> 00:14:05,000
and my creations.

160
00:14:08,279 --> 00:14:09,360
I won't let him be reckless.

161
00:14:14,159 --> 00:14:15,440
Are you spying on me?

162
00:14:16,039 --> 00:14:17,879
Are you spying on me, or am I spying on you?

163
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:19,879
Ridiculous.

164
00:15:11,679 --> 00:15:12,320
[Where are you?]

165
00:15:14,799 --> 00:15:15,559
[Let's meet up.]
